Problem Statement : You have been provided with a banking dataset that contains marketing insights for various campaigns that were run for the customers for a duration of time. Using your machine learning and analytical skills - provide actionable insights that will be useful for the company to plan striking and efficient marketing campaigns for their products. Dataset Information: Tasks To Be Performed: 1. Perform detailed EDA to obtain actionable insights for various features. 2. Perform Feature engineering and feature selection to reduce the noise from the data and prepare the data for data modeling. 3. Create a classification model using machine learning algorithms such as logistic regression, decision tree, random forest, etc. 4. Choose the best performing model, and optimize the efficiency of the model using hyperparameter tuning.
